You could have to clean up land contamination on your site before you can develop it. 

@FACT CHECK - IN WHAT CIRCUMSTANCES DO YOU NOT HAVE TO CLEAN UP CONTAMINATED LAND BEFORE DEVELOPING IT?@

Contact your [local council ](http://local.direct.gov.uk/LDGRedirect/index.jsp?mode=1.1 "Find your local council"){:rel="external"} to discuss planning and to check what you must do to make sure the land is suitable for your proposed development.
